Ready to take off on a splash-tactic adventure?
Buckle up for one of Australia’s most exhilarating boat rides, powered by a jaw-dropping 800 horsepower that’ll zip you right into the Great Barrier Reef Marine Park! In just 30 heart-pounding minutes, you’ll arrive at the vibrant shores of Daydream Island.
But the adventure’s only just beginning! Once you dock, you’ll join a marine biologist at the Living Reef for an up-close look at some of the reef’s most fascinating residents (valued at $55 per person!). Discover the unique behaviours of stingrays, sea stars and sea cucumbers, and learn how each plays a vital role in this incredible ecosystem.
After the marine magic, enjoy 45 minutes of free time to explore the island, grab a quick snack, or treat yourself to a refreshing beer or cocktail. Then, it’s time to hop back on the jet boat for a thrilling ride back to Airlie Beach!
